  "title": "RESTAURANT MANAGER",
  "description": "<p>In the restaurant manager role, you will facilitate an enjoyable and pleasurable dining experience for the restaurant’s patrons. As a restaurant manager, you will lead and train restaurant staff to ensure\nhigh-quality service is delivered. Success in this role will be demonstrated by your ability to grow the company’s profitability and customer base.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Develops innovative strategies that increase the establishment’s profitability</li><li>Ensures that the establishment is compliant with health and safety regulations</li><li>Conducts marketing efforts and hosts events</li><li>Sets work schedules to optimize staffing</li><li>Ensures inventory is well-stocked and efficiently utilized</li><li>Creates reports on daily, weekly, monthly, and annual restaurant operations</li><li>Handles customer concerns and suggestions</li></ul><p><strong>Qualifications:</strong></p><ul><li>Proven work experience as a Restaurant Manager</li><li>Excellent customer services skills</li><li>Basic knowledge of accounting and financial management</li><li>Deep knowledge of F&B industry</li><li>Strong leadership skills</li></ul>",
